Date: Sat, 23 May 2026 10:33:09 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 22/25] Cull stale popup traces

The logs grew thick as ivy vines,
They climbed through every popup line.
We pruned the noisy leaves away,
And left the fixes room to stay.
